query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 100 AND q.view_count <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-preferences',
'development-environment',
'disassembly',
'drawable',
'firebaseui',
'gensim',
'hashcode',
'python-3.4',
'static-members',
'twitter4j',
'unmanaged',
'vlookup',
'webcam',
'xib');
